        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Secure America's Financial Exchanges Act or the SAFE Act </strong></p> <p>This bill requires an issuer of securities, as a condition of listing its securities on a national exchange, to disclose (1) any financial support from China and the terms of any such support, and (2) whether any officer of director holds or previously held a position with the Chinese government or with the Chinese Communist Party. </p>]]>
        </text>
